Enchantment (Compulsion) [Mind-Affecting, Sonic]
Level: Brd 1, Hrp 1
Components: V, S
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: 30 ft.
Area: 30-ft.-radius burst centered on you
Duration: 1 round
Saving Throw: Will negates
Spell Resistance: Yes

You produce a crowd-stopping shout that holds an air of authority others find difficult to ignore.  The spell affects only those creatures that have 5HD or less.  Anyone affected is dazed for 1 round.